vip.floatationdevice.guilded4j.event

Class GuildedWebSocketClosedEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.EventObject
      • vip.floatationdevice.guilded4j.event.GuildedWebSocketClosedEvent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class GuildedWebSocketClosedEvent
extends java.util.EventObject
    Event that is fired when the event manager's WebSocket connection is closed. This is a Guilded4J's custom event, meaning that there is no event in the Guilded API called this name.
